import React from 'react' import Title from './Title'; import { services } from '../data'; const Services = () => { return (
<div className="section-center services-center"> {services.map((service) => { return ( <article className="service" key={service.id}> <span className="service-icon"> <i className={service.className}></i> </span> <div className="service-info"> <h4 className="service-title">{service.title}</h4> <p className="service-text"> {service.text} </p> </div> </article> ); })} <article className="service"> <span className="service-icon"> <i className="fas fa-tree fa-fw"></i> </span> <div className="service-info"> <h4 className="service-title">endless hiking</h4> <p className="service-text"> Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Asperiores, officia. </p> </div> </article> <article className="service"> <span className="service-icon"> <i className="fas fa-socks fa-fw"></i> </span> <div className="service-info"> <h4 className="service-title">amazing comfort</h4> <p className="service-text"> Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Asperiores, officia. </p> </div> </article> </div> </section> ); } export default Services
